title: Eat Local Co-operative
description: Provides local products many of which are organic. During the summer, fresh produce is available. Year-round stock include organic tempeh, frozen organic veggies, dried cranberries, peanut products, popping corn, potatoes, oats, flour, noodle, birch syrup, maple syrup, preserves, vinaigrette, soap, and more. Previously on Durham St.
